<MELItem itemNbr="52-36-03" id="X-BOEING:FTID:81205.787.DDG.CU.MEL.2-52-36-03.1.2-52-36-03">
<Title>Bulk Cargo Door Exterior Handle</Title>
<DispatchCondition repairInterval="C" nbrInstalled="1" nbrRequired="0" maintIndicator="(M)">
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>May be inoperative provided:</Para>
<List listType="a.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Interior handle operates normally.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Bulk cargo door indication operates normally.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Before each departure, bulk cargo door is verified closed, latched, and locked.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
<DispatchProcedure>
<MaintenanceProcedure>
<Para>Before each flight, verify that the door is closed, latched, and locked (AMM DDG 52-36-03).</Para>
<List listType="1.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Open and then close bulk cargo door using the interior handle.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Check that the door skin is aligned and faired with the fuselage skin.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Check that the latch handle is fully closed and faired with the door skin.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Push on the door to verify it is latched.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
<Para>Verify DOOR BULK CARGO advisory is not displayed.</Para>
</MaintenanceProcedure>
</DispatchProcedure>
</DispatchCondition>
</MELItem>
</DispatchItems>